4","image_QGYaCa"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"Create Your Own Spider  Light","description":"","text_align":"text-center","container":"container","background_color":"","layout_type":"carousel","column_gap":5,"aspect_ratio":"original","custom_ratio":"21:9","actions_click":"unset","custom_column":4,"grid_image_desktop":4,"autoplay":false,"loop":true,"show_arrow":true,"show_bullet":true,"show_bullet_mobile":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"banner_with_text_t8pnjn":{"type":"banner-with-text","blocks":{"text_PxTarN":{"type":"text","settings":{"txt_content":"<h2><br\/><br\/><strong>A pendant light does more than illuminate—it shapes the way we experience a room.<br\/>The right pendant light turns everyday moments into highlights.<\/strong><br\/><br\/><\/h2>","txt_color":"","txt_fs":16,"txt_fw":400,"txt_tf":"unset","txt_mt":0,"txt_mb":25}}},"block_order":["text_PxTarN"],"name":"Banner with text","settings":{"container":"container","background_color":"","banner_type":"image","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Untitled_design_10_14ef2687-eb28-47c7-886f-dce22b6a524e.jpg","video_options":"local","video_url":"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc","link":"","hover_effect":"zoom","bn_design":"text_column","banner_height":"depend-image","height_dk":800,"height_tb":600,"height_mb":360,"content_box":"content_in_container","text_bellow_mobile":false,"img_position":"left","banner_width":"col-md-6","column_gap":30,"text_horizontal_position":"left","text_position":"center","text_align":"text-center","content_width":100,"content_bg_color":"","bg_opacity":100,"eb_scrolling":false,"s_text_color":"#111111","s_text_font_size":80,"s_text_font_weight":600,"text_time":10,"text_spacing":50,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"custom_html_BEfkUx":{"type":"custom-html","settings":{"heading":"What is a Pendant Light?","description":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/pendant-lights\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/pendant-lights\">Pendant light<\/a> is a type of hanging ceiling light. You might compare it to a small lamp, except that instead of being perched atop a table, it hangs at the end of a cord, or chain, or metal rod.) Others refer to them as <a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/black-metal-ceiling-e27-conduit-pendant-light-fitting-holder-kit-5647\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/black-metal-ceiling-e27-conduit-pendant-light-fitting-holder-kit-5647\">hanging light<\/a>s, <a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/3-head-black-square-wire-cage-bar-triple-hanging-pendant-light\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/3-head-black-square-wire-cage-bar-triple-hanging-pendant-light\">drop lights<\/a> or<a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/8-way-spider-light-e27-pendant-light-adjustable-cable-with-swag-hook-for-kitchen-island-living-room-bedroom-bar-decor\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/8-way-spider-light-e27-pendant-light-adjustable-cable-with-swag-hook-for-kitchen-island-living-room-bedroom-bar-decor\"> suspender lights.<\/a><\/p><p>Pendant lights are found in homes, businesses, restaurants, and much more. They look great and give great lighting so very popular choice for interior design.<\/p>","text_alignment":"text-left","container":"container","background_color":"","content_html":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"custom_html_JpTBFD":{"type":"custom-html","settings":{"heading":"Types of Pendant Lighting","description":"<p>Modern pendant lighting are very flexible, and they can be used in different ways depending on the type of light they provide:<\/p><ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/pendant-lights?page=3\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/pendant-lights?page=3\"><strong>Task Lighting<\/strong> <\/a>– These lights shine directly onto a workspace. They are great for kitchen counters, reading nooks, or office desks. A good example is a <a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/2-head-lamp-ceiling-pendant-light-adjustable-cord-shade-5034\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/2-head-lamp-ceiling-pendant-light-adjustable-cord-shade-5034\">downlight pendant<\/a>, which has an open bottom to direct light downward.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/pendant-lights?page=5\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/pendant-lights?page=5\"><strong>Ambient Lighting<\/strong> <\/a>– This type of lighting spreads across a room. <a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/turkish-moroccan-mosaic-tiles-crackle-pattern-bulb-shape-pendant-light\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/turkish-moroccan-mosaic-tiles-crackle-pattern-bulb-shape-pendant-light\">Inverted pendant lights<\/a> shine light upwards, making them useful in dining areas and hallways.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/pendant-lights?page=35\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/pendant-lights?page=35\"><strong>Accent Lighting<\/strong><\/a> – While Hanging light fixtures are not the best for highlighting specific objects, they can still be used to draw attention to a certain area in a room.<\/li><\/ul>","text_alignment":"text-left","container":"container","background_color":"","content_html":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"custom_html_zgQ4NK":{"type":"custom-html","settings":{"heading":"Pendant Lights vs. Chandeliers","description":"<p>Some people confuse<a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/pendant-lights?page=33\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/pendant-lights?page=33\"> Statement pendant lighting<\/a> with chandeliers because both hang from the ceiling. However, there is a key difference:<\/p><ul><li><strong>Pendant lights<\/strong> usually have one bulb.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/chandelier\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/chandelier\"><strong>Chandeliers<\/strong><\/a> have multiple bulbs arranged in a decorative way.<\/li><\/ul><p>Chandeliers are more formal and are often used in dining rooms or entryways, while <a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/pendant-lights?page=32\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/pendant-lights?page=32\">contemporary pendant lights<\/a> can be used in many different settings for both function and style.<\/p>","text_alignment":"text-left","container":"container","background_color":"","content_html":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"collection_list_TJYnD8":{"type":"collection-list","blocks":{"collection_item_Chrwm3":{"type":"collection_item","settings":{"title_collection":"","collection":"pendant-lights","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/s-l1600_1_34247eb5-d11e-4073-8414-8ef94ce4e6d8.webp"}},"collection_item_qw6Czm":{"type":"collection_item","settings":{"title_collection":"","collection":"chandelier","image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/ModernChandeliersCrystalwithLight_ChromeCrystalChanderlierLighting11.webp"}}},"block_order":["collection_item_Chrwm3","collection_item_qw6Czm"],"name":"Collection list","settings":{"heading":"","description":"","text_alignment":"text-center","container":"container","background_color":"","design_layout":"carousel","design_collection":"design-1","hover_effect":"zoom","show_count_product":true,"custom_width_images":false,"width_image":200,"images_style":"square","image_ratio":"3\/4","custom_ratio":"21:9","custom_column":6,"column_gap":30,"autoplay":false,"loop":false,"show_arrow":false,"show_bullet":false,"show_bullet_mobile":false,"reveal_on_scroll":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"custom_html_z4DWEp":{"type":"custom-html","settings":{"heading":"Where to Use Pendant Lights?","description":"<p>Adjustable hanging lights can be placed in many parts of a home or office, including:<\/p><ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/kitchen-lights-for-over-table\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/kitchen-lights-for-over-table\"><strong>Kitchen<\/strong><\/a> – Over kitchen islands or counters for<a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/industrial-20mm-conduit-pipe-wall-lighting-kit-5701\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/industrial-20mm-conduit-pipe-wall-lighting-kit-5701\"> focused lighting<\/a>.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/living-or-dining-room-lighting\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/living-or-dining-room-lighting\"><strong>Dining Room<\/strong><\/a> – Above a dining table to create a cozy atmosphere.<\/li><li><strong>Hallways<\/strong> – For general lighting and decoration.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/conduit-lighting-1\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/conduit-lighting-1\"><strong>Workspaces<\/strong><\/a> – Above desks or workbenches for better visibility.<\/li><\/ul>","text_alignment":"text-left","container":"container","background_color":"","content_html":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"gallery_6NiqaQ":{"type":"gallery","blocks":{"image_DbQAXG":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/A2_2__12_11zon.webp","link":"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/pendant-long-tube-light-modern-cylinder-pipe-contemporary-4599"}},"image_yhtCkw":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/3_light_kitchen_and_dining_room_lighting_e6dc48fd-ca39-49a2-ab9c-910f7769cc05.webp","link":"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/3-light-pendant-light-fixture-bulb-guard-cage"}},"image_AykaAQ":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Metal-vintage-lampshade-5.jpg","link":"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/vintage-black-metal-lampshadependant-ceiling-light"}},"image_B3ARmT":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/nd5app3_5_11zon_5_11zon_19985379-60e6-4550-bf0d-d1c11a73cf17.webp","link":"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/3-light-multiple-colour-pendant-light-flex-swag-hook"}}},"block_order":["image_DbQAXG","image_yhtCkw","image_AykaAQ","image_B3ARmT"],"settings":{"heading":"","description":"","text_align":"text-center","container":"container","background_color":"","layout_type":"carousel","column_gap":30,"aspect_ratio":"original","custom_ratio":"21:9","actions_click":"unset","custom_column":3,"grid_image_desktop":4,"autoplay":false,"loop":false,"show_arrow":false,"show_bullet":true,"show_bullet_mobile":false,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"custom_html_FHBhyB":{"type":"custom-html","settings":{"heading":"Choosing the Right Pendant Light","description":"","text_alignment":"text-center","container":"container","background_color":"","content_html":"<table class=\"table\">\n            <tbody>\n<tr>\n                <th><b>Factor<\/b><\/th>\n                <th><b>Consideration <\/b><\/th>\n            <\/tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td><strong>Size<\/strong><\/td>\n                <td>A mini pendant lights might get lost in a large room, while a big one could be overwhelming in a small space.<\/td>\n            <\/tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td><strong>Height<\/strong><\/td>\n                <td>Ensure the light hangs at the right level. Too low, and people might bump their heads; too high, and it may not provide enough illumination.<\/td>\n            <\/tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td><strong>Brightness<\/strong><\/td>\n                <td>Some hanging lights use dimmable bulbs, allowing you to control the brightness based on your needs.<\/td>\n            <\/tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td><strong>Style<\/strong><\/td>\n                <td>ceiling pendants come in various designs, from modern glass fixtures to vintage metal lamps. Choose one that complements your space.<\/td>\n            <\/tr>\n        <\/tbody>\n<\/table>","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"custom_html_t3hGr4":{"type":"custom-html","settings":{"heading":"How to install pendant lights?","description":"","text_alignment":"text-center","container":"container","background_color":"","content_html":"<iframe width=\"500\" height=\"400\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/videos\/c\/o\/v\/8d57bc42b9954bab975403a11e523f1c.mp4\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"><\/iframe>","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}},"faq_yYwCdV":{"type":"faq","blocks":{"faq_TedpUz":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"Which ceiling pendant lights are best for a living room?","content":"<p>When choosing the best<a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/3-way-industrial-conduit-pipe-ceiling-pendant-diy-light-fixture\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">ceiling pendant lights<\/span><\/a> for your living room, black pendant lights are a stylish and versatile option.Pendant lights for the living room hang from the ceiling, often suspended by cords, chains, or fixed rods for added stability. They come in a variety of designs, from sleek, single-bulb styles to more elaborate multi-branch fixtures.<\/p><p>The popularity of<a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/industrial-retro-loft-glass-3way-ceiling-lamp-shade-pendant-light-5607\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> industrial pendant light fixtures<\/span><\/a> in living rooms comes down to their adaptability. They can enhance any space with both modern and traditional aesthetics. Many<a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/black-metal-ceiling-e27-conduit-pendant-light-fitting-holder-kit-5647\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">adjustable pendant lights<\/span><\/a>, allowing you to customize the lighting  heights for your living room’s specific needs. Some designs, like Rise and Fall lights, even allow you to easily change the height for a dynamic lighting effect. <\/p>"}},"faq_wLr4Ka":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"What are some best high-quality modern dining room lights?","content":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/living-or-dining-room-lighting\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Dining Room Pendant Lights<\/span><\/a> are a great alternative for modern lighting for your dining room; they combine beauty and usability. Among my top picks are:<\/p><p><a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/hemp-rope-pendant-light\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Hanging lights<\/span><\/a>: perfect for providing a strong statement in your dining room, these flexible fittings have a sophisticated and svelte look. Hung at varying heights, they produce an impressive visual effect.<\/p><p>For a one-of-a-kind and personalized dinner, consider unique pendant lighting. Available in several shapes, materials, and styles, these allow you to select a fixture that really reflects your own style.<\/p><p>Modern dining areas often favor pendant light designs, among many styles that complement contemporary decor. Whether it's quiet or eye-catching, you may choose a style that matches the feel of your room.<\/p><p>These pendant light fittings hang from the ceiling and are great for adding ambient or functional lighting to your dining area. Various textiles including metal, glass, and fabric are available; therefore the design possibilities are many.<\/p>"}},"faq_iAUh7g":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"How can decorative lighting enhance a room's ambiance?","content":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/modern-chandelier-led-crystal-ceiling-mount-and-hanging-light-5423\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Ornamental lighting<\/span><\/a>, if used right, will make so much change in the mood of a room through the infusing of style and functionality.<a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/black-2-light-holder\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Hanging lights<\/span><\/a> or even pendant light fittings provide an area of focus that is elegant and may completely change the feel of a room. More unique pendant lights, such as an offset pendant light or<a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/3-head-black-square-wire-cage-bar-triple-hanging-pendant-light\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">3-light cluster pendant<\/span><\/a>, bring a touch of sophistication and drama, hence perfect for the living room or dining area.<\/p><p>From pendant light fixtures to ceiling hanging, their versatile styles can fit many room sizes and décor themes. A 3-light bar pendant ceiling light or 3-light hanging fixture in a modern style would be perfect for larger rooms, as they distribute light evenly and add aesthetic value to the room. Kitchen pendant lighting, especially in the UK, illuminates your work areas in style.<\/p><p>In commercial settings, office pendant lights offer a compelling blend of form and function. They deliver focused illumination for workspaces without overwhelming the overall aesthetic of the space. Selecting the ideal decorative light fitting, such as a three-light hanging lamp or a three-light ceiling light, can significantly enhance the ambiance and visual appeal of any room, contributing to a more productive and welcoming environment.<\/p>"}},"faq_WrwNBc":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"How to light a dark living room ceiling light?","content":"<p>To light a dark living room, consider:<\/p><ul><li>Adding <strong>recessed lighting<\/strong> to create ambient light.<\/li><li>Using <strong>wall sconces<\/strong> or <strong>floor lamps<\/strong> in addition to overhead lights.<\/li><li>Install dimmable <strong>pendant lights<\/strong> or <strong>track lighting<\/strong> for flexibility.<\/li><\/ul>"}},"faq_E3h48U":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"Do Pendant Lights Make a Room Look Smaller?","content":"<p>No, pendant lights do not necessarily make a room look smaller. In fact, the right pendant lights can enhance the perception of space by drawing the eye upward and creating a sense of height. However, choosing the right size, placement, and style is key to maintaining a balanced look.<\/p><p>For example,<a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/products\/metal-kitchen-pendant-light\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> black hanging ceiling lights<\/span><\/a><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> <\/span>and black hanging lamps can add a sleek, modern touch without overwhelming a space. Meanwhile, glass ball pendant lights reflect light beautifully, making a room feel more open and airy. If you have a lower ceiling, semi-flush ceiling lights or antique brass hanging lamps can offer a similar aesthetic without taking up too much visual space.<\/p>"}},"faq_pNFVMj":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"Should pendant lights be centered to the kitchen island?","content":"<p>Yes,<a href=\"https:\/\/ledsone.co.uk\/collections\/kitchen-lights-for-over-table\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">pendant lights<\/span><\/a> should generally be centered over a kitchen island to provide balanced lighting and enhance the overall aesthetics of the space. Proper placement ensures even illumination for tasks like cooking and dining while maintaining a visually appealing look.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["faq_TedpUz","faq_wLr4Ka","faq_iAUh7g","faq_WrwNBc","faq_E3h48U","faq_pNFVMj"],"settings":{"heading":"Frequently Asked Questions","description":"","text_alignment":"text-center","container":"container","background_color":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"reset_spacing":false}}},"order":["main","banner_image_JYPtCK","image_comparison_BFpw4r","collection_packery_JWVLiA","banner_with_text_Hn3m3H","banner_with_text_DGg9Ht","banner_with_text_7M73TD","banner_with_text_LLRFqH","banner_with_text_e6kjtY","banner_with_text_bXRXHa","gallery_688iyW","gallery_8P3nw4","banner_with_text_t8pnjn","custom_html_BEfkUx","custom_html_JpTBFD","custom_html_zgQ4NK","collection_list_TJYnD8","custom_html_z4DWEp","gallery_6NiqaQ","custom_html_FHBhyB","custom_html_t3hGr4","faq_yYwCdV"]}